{"tid":1235582,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣呼籲] 重申修例惡處 重攻Offline廢老及中年","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T07:42:22.000Z","uid":58041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d53ead210c2dab39ea38ea3f66a4714422796499","tid":1235582,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"Online Coverage我地可以自己做到<br />\n但係Offline Media既亦威力不宜被小看<br />\n<br />\n2019年五月Facebook香港用戶總人數：4,584,000<br />\n只佔總人口61%<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://napoleoncat.com/stats/facebook-users-in-hong_kong/2019/05\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnapoleoncat.com%2Fstats%2Ffacebook-users-in-hong_kong%2F2019%2F05&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=04533df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://napoleoncat.com/stats/facebook-users-in-hong_kong/2019/05</a><br />\n(求其搵，但想指出網絡coverage係好大，可惜未必係你想像中咁大）<br />\n<br />\n現正呼籲各界人士<br />\n重申修例惡處 滲入社區<br />\n傳單/痴紙係好方法 亦可口傳/借記者把口重申<br />\n記得抖夠再做如果唔係會辛苦<br />\n<br />\n要用民情不斷上漲作為武器<br />\n<br />\nTo依家有野做緊既人<br />\n唔緊要，你一定抽到時間幫手<br />\n香港人，齊心！"},{"pid":"c75d7209c30cbaeceb65f605567e21b601dfe6f3","tid":1235582,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"32f45eedc98a6a39f40b5f809f480af0bd340129","tid":1235582,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n<br />\nBtw <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，<br />\n百花齊放，殊途同歸，<br />\n槍口對外，絕不分化，<br />\n爭取自由，天經地義，<br />\n百萬加一，勿忘義士。</span></span>"},{"pid":"350b22f88dc8f7cc2c4e26d714b24233c6406e94","tid":1235582,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}